sentences: Rie (理衣, Rie, born 14 August 1980 in Tokyo) is a Japanese fashion model.
She also has appeared in commercial for companies such as Toyota or Sapporo Beverage and in the 2006 movie Memories of Matsuko (though uncredited).
In 2007 she appeared on Remioromen's videoclip for Akanezora.
In 2009 she married a businessman from Hong Kong.
In late 2011, she announced she was pregnant.
